---
title: Drizzly Balsamic Fig Chicken with Sweet Potatoes and Arugula
description: We're big fans of pan sauces because they're a simple way to add extra flavor to dishes. Here, fig jam, balsamic vinegar, and fresh rosemary are allowed to mingle with the natural juices from the chicken to create a sweet and savory condiment that you'll want to drizzle over everything.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-chicken-with-fig-balsamic-ba96cfd2.jpg
